<h2>viewers analysis</h2>joshua<br>
<h1>People stream movies and tv shows because of the flexibility of the amount of content they can watch and for the ability to watch older titles fulfilling a want to feel nostalgia.<br>People stream podcasts to listen to their favorite celebrities talk about a certain topics for a few hours.<br>People stream music videos to uplift their mood.<br>People watch vlogs to see what their favorite vloggers do in their daily life.<br>People watch gaming streams for a lot of reasons, one of which is the social aspect of interacting with your favorite streamers. Just even hearing a big celebrity with millions of followers call you by name is enough to make a grown man cry out in excitement.
And of course, to get better at the game they are watching.
</h1>
